name: I can't stop thinking about how badly I did.

speech: I understand how worrying this must feel, but overthinking won’t change the past. Let’s focus on what you can control moving forward.
It’s okay to feel anxious about results, but remember, you’ve done your best, and that’s all anyone can ask for
The outcome isn’t the end of the story. There’s always a way forward, no matter what. Let’s think about how to tackle the next step.
